  m_text: "Quick Guide to Bonus Shop:\n\nGold: Exchange Rubies for Gold. \n(Conversion
    Rate of 1 Ruby = 100 Gold.)\n\nRuby Amulet: More Rubies earned upon finishing
    next run.\n\nRobo-Hero: Automatically damages the enemy with your base damage.\n\nNew
    Game+ Voucher: Allows you to carry over gold and upgrades upon dying, once.\n(Max
    of 1).\n\nCommerorative Plushie: Does nothing! Proof of mastery or of time wasting
    capabilities.\n(Max of 1)."
