  m_text: 'Quick Guide to Standard Shop:


    Sword Reforge: More base damage per
    click.


    Magic Stopwatch: More time bonus time every 10th wave.


    Training
    Manual: Add on more chance for a weak spot to appear.

    (Max of 50)


    Assassin''s
    Lens: More damage added on weak point hit.


    Crude Golem: 3 * Upgrade Tier
    passive damage to enemy.


    Gold Charm: More gold earned for doing anything.'
